### Задание 5.5 — Прибыль за указанный год

```sql
DELIMITER //
CREATE FUNCTION get_profit_by_year(p_year INT)
RETURNS DECIMAL(10,2)
DETERMINISTIC
READS SQL DATA
BEGIN
    DECLARE result DECIMAL(10,2);
    
    SELECT SUM(b.price * oi.quantity)
    INTO result
    FROM order_items oi
    JOIN books b ON oi.book_id = b.book_id
    JOIN orders o ON oi.order_id = o.order_id
    WHERE YEAR(o.order_datetime) = p_year;
    
    RETURN result;
END //
DELIMITER ;

-- Проверка:
SELECT get_profit_by_year(2024);
```

